# Secrets Configuration for Streamlit Cloud

To run this application on Streamlit Cloud, you need to configure the following secrets:

## Required Secrets

Go to your app settings on Streamlit Cloud and add these in the "Secrets" section:

```toml
# Google Gemini API Key (required for memo generation)
GEMINI_API_KEY = "your-gemini-api-key-here"

# Semantic Scholar API Key (optional, but recommended to avoid rate limits)
SEMANTIC_SCHOLAR_API_KEY = "your-semantic-scholar-api-key-here"
```

## How to Get API Keys

### Google Gemini API Key
1. Go to https://ai.google.dev/
2. Click "Get API key in Google AI Studio"
3. Create a new API key
4. Copy and paste it into Streamlit secrets

### Semantic Scholar API Key (Optional)
1. Go to https://www.semanticscholar.org/product/api
2. Request an API key
3. Copy and paste it into Streamlit secrets

## Note
Without these keys, the application will have limited functionality. The Gemini API key is essential for generating policy memos.
